data.description: Beautiful Spacious Corner Townhouse with 3 Bedrooms, 2.5 Baths, Living Room, High Ceilings, Open Concept Kitchen, Large Bedrooms, 1 Car Garage, Extended Driveway for 3+ Vehicles, Oversized Backyard that is perfect for pets, children, and/or entertaining, and much more!! The property is located in the highly sought-after MANDARIN LAKES! Resort-style living with incredible amenities including an Olympic-size pool, playgrounds, a fitness center, and a business center. The community is quiet and safe with 24 hour security. The location is convenient and close to the turnpike, shopping, restaurants, schools and more. Call us today for your private tour of this incredible property!
